{"tid":1998764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"只要你唔犯法，何需怕逃犯條例？","createTime":"2020-05-02T15:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T16:22:08.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6d38304995e060d3a124f3c7fc3f8e072ca44c","tid":1998764,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:47:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">世衛駐華代表︰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中方拒絕世衛參與調查病毒來源</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=389523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389523&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=93db69e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389523&h=8da2aede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=389523</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】世衛駐華代表高力表示，世衛多次要求參與調查新型冠狀病毒來源，但遭到中方拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n高力接受英國天空新聞訪問，指知道中方已經開始就新型冠狀病毒疫情進行調查，但未有邀請世衛參與。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>而世衛多次向中方衞生部門要求加入調查工作，但都被中方在<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>沒有合理原因下拒絕</ins></span>。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n高力強調，調查清楚病毒來源以及動物透過甚麼媒介將病毒傳給人類，對防止再次發生疫情非常重要。他又指根據世衛現時得到的資料顯示，病毒源自武漢，相信是自然變種，而非人為製造出來的病毒。"},{"pid":"fdc0a8a9600a305397aa5a1fd37bccfb9bef2144","tid":1998764,"uid":64031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"香港警察也說自己沒有犯法<br />\n但堅決反對成立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n不是怕<br />\n而是一定犯了法"}]}